# signal-canary-deploy

Post-deploy health canary. See signal-setup-deploy.mdc for full lifecycle.

## When to use
- After deploying: `signalos signal-canary-deploy --wave 12`

## Key behaviours
- Returns count of deploy records for the given wave
- `found: false` and `count: 0` if no records or index missing
